sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Notely
    participant ASR
    participant OCR
    participant LLM

    User->>Notely: Initialize with API key
    User->>Notely: process(video_path)

    Notely->>Notely: Extract audio & frames

    Notely->>ASR: Transcribe audio
    ASR-->>Notely: Transcript with timestamps

    Notely->>OCR: Recognize text from frames
    OCR-->>Notely: Extracted text

    Notely->>LLM: Generate notes (transcript + OCR)
    LLM-->>Notely: Structured Markdown

    Notely->>Notely: Format & beautify
    Notely-->>User: NotelyResult

    User->>Notely: result.save("notes.md")
    Notely-->>User: ✓ Saved
